long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you tired of the same old boring new tab page? Do you want to add some humor to your day? Look no further! Our product is here to bring a smile to your face every time you open a new tab. With our carefully curated selection of geek jokes, you’ll never have a dull moment again.

Not only will our product bring some much-needed humor to your day, but it’s also incredibly easy to use. No complicated settings or configurations - just install and go. And if you ever get tired of the jokes (although we doubt you will), it’s just as easy to uninstall.

So why wait? Add some humor to your day with our product. You won’t regret it.
